7. How the Two Use Cases Will Consume the Data
Use Case 1 – Incident Pulse
URL traceroute service already exists → returns device/IP list.
Backend endpoint: /api/incident-pulse/triage?deviceId=XYZ
Logic: Query MongoDB for open incidents/changes where cmdbCi.name or affectedCis matches the device.
Return correlated list + CPU/mem overlay.
Use Case 2 – Enterprise Critical Products
New Angular page filters by Business Function / Flow.
Backend joins snow_service_mappings with internal Flow/Business Function mapping table.
Shows active Incidents & Changes with impact score.
